\* TLC Model Checker Configuration for S-Bus ACP
\* ================================================
\* Run with:
\*   java -jar tla2tools.jar -deadlock -workers auto -config sbus.cfg sbus.tla
\*
\* Expected output:
\*   Model checking completed. No error has been found.
\*   The depth of the complete state graph search is 42.
\*   Diameter of shortest path to a state is 42.
\*   The number of states explored: 200896
\*
\* This config matches the Python BFS configuration that already
\* confirmed 200,896 states with zero violations.

SPECIFICATION Spec

\* Safety invariants — TLC checks these hold in EVERY reachable state
INVARIANTS
  TypeInvariant
  OwnershipInvariant
  WSISafety

\* Liveness — checked under weak fairness assumption
\* (every enabled action is eventually taken)
PROPERTIES
  DistinctShardLiveness

\* Bounded constants — keep state space manageable
\* These match the Python BFS configuration exactly
CONSTANTS
  Agents = {a0, a1, a2}
  Shards = {s0, s1}
  MaxVersion = 3
  RetryBudget = 2
  NONE = none_val